summary: Next in my series of retextures to match my heroic dwarven armor.
descriptionHtml:
The second weapon I\'ve retextured to match my Heroic Dwarven Armor (http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=4499)

Have also done the dwarven arrows (at the same link as the armor) and the dwarven bow: http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=4515

I\'ll be working through the shield and the rest of the weapons next.
